es of this </div><div class="t m209 x63 h15 yc33 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">life, however severe, are minor compared with the total joy and fulfillment </div><div class="t m66d x63 h15 y1a2 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the afterlife. &quot;For </div><div class="t m277 x95 h19 y1a2 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I </div><div class="t m435 x10 h15 y1a2 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reckon that the sufferings of this present time are </div><div class="t m4c4 x63 h15 yc16 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not worthy to be compared with the glory which shall be revealed in us&quot; </div><div class="t mc1 x63 h15 y1a4 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rom. 8:18). </div><div class="t m5c x86 h19 yb00 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">OVERVIEW: Revelation 21:1-22:21 </div><div class="t m128 x45 h19 y930 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">21:1-4 </div><div class="t m33f x23 h19 y930 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">21:5-8 </div><div class="t m66e x30 h19 y930 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">21:9-22:5 </div><div class="t m1c8 x2a h15 yc34 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A new heaven and </div><div class="t m31 x6b h15 ybd6 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a new earth </div><div class="t m42 x7b h15 yc34 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jesus completes </div><div class="t m294 x4b h15 ybd6 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His work of salvation </div><div class="t m307 x2d h15 yc35 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The New Jerusalem </div><div class="t m6e x84 h15 yc36 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">described </div><div class="t m2ac xe6 h19 y328 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">EPILOGUE: Jesus is Coming (Rev. 22:7-21) </div><div class="t m3f2 x13 h19 y7fd ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">EYE HAS NOT SEEN. </div><div class="t m66f x7b h15 y7fd ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">An elderly Christian had been confined to a </div><div class="t mf2 x13 h15 y7fe ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">wheel chair for forty-three years. His Seventh-day Adventist Christianity </div><div class="t m5c7 x13 h15 yc37 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">had a powerful influence on those around him, and especially on his grand-</div><div class="t mc